3. **`| sqlgen::where("value"_c > 100)`** - Applies the WHERE condition using the pipe operator to filter records where value > 100
4. **`sqlgen::create_as<Target>(select_query)`** - Creates the CREATE TABLE AS SELECT statement that will create the Target table from the filtered SELECT query

